-e-fuentes-rohwer/\",\"displayName\":\"Luis E. Fuentes-Rohwer\",\"id\":\"Author:26964\",\"slug\":\"luis-e-fuentes-rohwer\",\"__typename\":\"Author\"}],\"riverImage\":{\"id\":\"Image:1549182:80x80:1x,2x\",\"url\":\"https://cdn.theatlantic.com/thumbor/rM0-IaryKCU_Sn7w96KBBuUYj94=/438x0:1563x1125/80x80/media/img/mt/2021/07/VRA_AZ/original.jpg\",\"srcSet\":\"https://cdn.theatlantic.com/thumbor/rM0-IaryKCU_Sn7w96KBBuUYj94=/438x0:1563x1125/80x80/media/img/mt/2021/07/VRA_AZ/original.jpg, https://cdn.theatlantic.com/thumbor/mC8bFeF5rRY26pP7IXpmQE6ntjI=/438x0:1563x1125/160x160/media/img/mt/2021/07/VRA_AZ/original.jpg 2x\",\"width\":80,\"height\":80,\"altText\":\"Artwork of a gavel smashing a seal commemorating the Voting Rights Act\",\"__typename\":\"BasicImage\"},\"__typename\":\"BlogArticle\"},\"__typename\":\"PromoEdge\"},{\"node\":{\"url\":\"https://www.theatlantic.com/ideas/archive/2021/06/hate-crimes-not-used-prosecutors/619179/\",\"title\":\"Hate-Crime Laws Don’t Work as Their Supporters Intended\",\"authors\":[{\"url\":\"https://www.theatlantic.com/author/avlana-eisenberg/\",\"displayName\":\"Avlana Eisenberg\",\"id\":\"Author:26923\",\"slug\":\"avlana-eisenberg\",\"__typename\":\"Author\"}],\"riverImage\":{\"id\":\"Image:1547972:80x80:1x,2x\",\"url\":\"https://cdn.theatlantic.com/thumbor/7cUEeEqRGlgnEhnDvdg1y14T8to=/234x0:810x576/80x80/media/img/mt/2021/06/Image_from_iOS_27/original.jpg\",\"srcSet\":\"https://cdn.theatlantic.com/thumbor/7cUEeEqRGlgnEhnDvdg1y14T8to=/234x0:810x576/80x80/media/img/mt/2021/06/Image_from_iOS_27/original.jpg, https://cdn.theatlantic.com/thumbor/fX8aEq6R8Jsv1byDifNC9J_iOCs=/234x0:810x576/160x160/media/img/mt/2021/06/Image_from_iOS_27/original.jpg 2x\",\"width\":80,\"height\":80,\"altText\":\"An illustration of a box that says \\\"Break glass in case of hate\\\" with a gavel inside\",\"__typename\":\"BasicImage\"},\"__typename\":\"BlogArticle\"},\"__typename\":\"PromoEdge\"},{\"node\":{\"url\":\"https://www.theatlantic.com/ideas/archive/202